    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Culture of an indigenous Pre-Columbian people who were a hunting society and a subdivision of the Ona of the Patagonian region of southern Argentina and Chile, including the Tierra del Fuego islands. Now virtually extinct.</Note_Text>
